  => "T1: |> verify_by script. T2: header expr nonempty + ==/~>/=> continuation. T4: !! breakthrough marker. T5: {@C,@R,@F,@L,@S} definitional + numeric-derivation header expr + verified deps."
  => "Type discipline: definitional types {@C,@R,@F,@L,@S} admit T5; primitive {@P}, crossing {@X}, unknown {@?} require explicit derivation continuation."
  => "Fixpoint loop: entry whose only blocker is unverified [10] dep can become eligible after dep promotes in earlier round."
  |> state/atlas_promotion_plan_20260425.md §Methodology

